<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Day 1 — Welcome to the Unmuted Voice Challenge</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;0,900;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --ink: #1a1018;
  --cream: #faf6f0;
  --warm: #f2e8d8;
  --accent: #c9462e;
  --accent2: #e8a030;
  --muted: #7a6e6a;
  --safe: #4a8c5c;
  --card-bg: #ffffff;
  --border: rgba(26,16,24,0.08);
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}

body {
  background: var(--cream);
  color: var(--ink);
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 1.7;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* ─── SLIDE ENGINE ─── */
.slides-wrapper {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
}

.slide {
  min-height: 100vh;
  width: 100%;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 80px 40px 60px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(24px);
  transition: opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease;
}
.slide.active { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

/* ─── HEADER BAR ─── */
header {
  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 56px;
  background: rgba(250,246,240,0.96);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 0 32px;
  z-index: 200;
}
.logo {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--accent);
}
.day-badge {
  background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream);
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  padding: 5px 14px; text-transform: uppercase;
}
.nav-pills {
  display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;
}
.pill {
  width: 28px; height: 5px; border-radius: 3px;
  background: #d0c8c0; cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}
.pill.active { background: var(--accent); width: 40px; }
.pill.done { background: var(--accent2); }

/* ─── PROGRESS ─── */
#prog {
  position: fixed; top: 56px; left: 0; height: 2px;
  background: var(--accent); z-index: 201;
  transition: width 0.4s ease;
}

/* ─── NAV ARROWS ─── */
.nav-arrow {
  position: fixed; bottom: 32px;
  background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream);
  border: none; cursor: pointer;
  width: 48px; height: 48px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 18px; z-index: 200;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}
.nav-arrow:hover { background: var(--accent); }
#nav-prev { left: 40px; }
#nav-next { right: 40px; }
.slide-counter {
  position: fixed; bottom: 38px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
  font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--muted);
  z-index: 200; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
}

/* ─── TYPOGRAPHY ─── */
.label {
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.label-accent { color: var(--accent); }
h1 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: clamp(40px, 7vw, 80px);
  font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.05;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}
h2 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 52px);
  font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.15;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
h3 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.lead { font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.65; color: #3d3035; max-width: 640px; }
p.body { font-size: 15px; color: #3d3035; max-width: 640px; }

.accent-text { color: var(--accent); }
.italic { font-style: italic; }
.strong { font-weight: 700; }

/* ─── SLIDE 1: HERO ─── */
#s1 {
  background: var(--ink);
  background-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 20%, rgba(201,70,46,0.18) 0%, transparent 55%),
                    radial-gradient(ellipse at 10% 80%, rgba(232,160,48,0.08) 0%, transparent 45%);
}
#s1 h1 { color: var(--cream); }
#s1 .label { color: var(--accent); }
#s1 .body { color: #b8a4a0; max-width: 580px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; }
.hero-rule { width: 48px; height: 3px; background: var(--accent); margin: 20px 0; }
.theme-pill {
  display: inline-flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center;
  border: 1px solid rgba(201,70,46,0.4);
  padding: 10px 20px; margin-bottom: 32px;
  font-size: 13px; color: #e0c8c0; font-style: italic;
}
.day-number {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: clamp(100px, 20vw, 200px);
  font-weight: 900; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  position: absolute; right: -20px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%);
  line-height: 1; pointer-events: none; user-select: none;
}
.btn {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  background: var(--accent); color: white;
  padding: 13px 28px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;
  cursor: pointer; border: none; margin-top: 24px;
  transition: all 0.2s; letter-spacing: 0.03em;
}
.btn:hover { background: #a8382a; transform: translateY(-1px); }

/* ─── SLIDE 2: WHAT TO EXPECT ─── */
#s2 { background: var(--cream); }
.expect-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 20px; margin-top: 36px; max-width: 900px;
}
.expect-card {
  background: white; padding: 24px;
  border-top: 3px solid transparent;
  opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px);
  transition: opacity 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease, border-color 0.3s;
}
.expect-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); }
.expect-card.show { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.ec-num {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 36px; font-weight: 900;
  color: rgba(201,70,46,0.15); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.expect-card h4 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.expect-card p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); max-width: none; margin: 0; }

/* ─── SLIDE 3: JOURNEY MAP ─── */
#s3 { background: #f5f0ea; }
.journey-track {
  display: flex; align-items: center;
  gap: 0; margin-top: 40px; max-width: 860px; width: 100%;
  position: relative; flex-wrap: nowrap;
  overflow-x: auto; padding-bottom: 16px;
}
.jstep {
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
  flex: 1; min-width: 100px;
  opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px);
  transition: opacity 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease;
}
.jstep.show { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.jnode {
  width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 18px; font-weight: 900; position: relative;
  z-index: 2; flex-shrink: 0; cursor: default;
  transition: transform 0.2s ease;
}
.jnode:hover { transform: scale(1.1); }
.jnode.current { background: var(--accent); color: white; box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(201,70,46,0.2); }
.jnode.upcoming { background: white; color: var(--muted); border: 2px solid #ddd; }
.jconnect {
  flex: 1; height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--accent), #ddd);
  margin-top: -26px; z-index: 1;
}
.jlabel {
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 10px; text-align: center;
  color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  max-width: 80px; line-height: 1.3;
}
.jlabel.now { color: var(--accent); }

/* ─── SLIDE 4: THE CORE MESSAGE ─── */
#s4 { background: var(--ink); }
#s4 h2 { color: var(--cream); }
.big-quote {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: clamp(22px, 3.5vw, 40px);
  font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.3;
  color: var(--cream); max-width: 760px;
  position: relative; padding-left: 28px;
}
.big-quote::before {
  content: '"';
  position: absolute; left: 0; top: -8px;
  font-size: 60px; color: var(--accent); line-height: 1;
}
.quote-label {
  margin-top: 24px; font-size: 13px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
}
.two-path {
  display: flex; gap: 20px; margin-top: 40px; max-width: 840px;
}
.path-card {
  flex: 1; padding: 24px;
  opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-16px);
  transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
}
.path-card.show { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
.path-card:nth-child(2) { transition-delay: 0.2s; transform: translateX(16px); }
.path-card:nth-child(2).show { transform: translateX(0); }
.path-card.bad { background: rgba(201,70,46,0.1); border-top: 3px solid var(--accent); }
.path-card.good { background: rgba(74,140,92,0.12); border-top: 3px solid var(--safe); }
.path-icon { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.path-card h4 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 8px; }
.path-card p { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); max-width: none; }

/* ─── SLIDE 5: WHY EXCITEMENT FAILS ─── */
#s5 { background: var(--cream); }
.fuel-diagram {
  display: flex; gap: 32px; align-items: flex-start;
  margin-top: 40px; flex-wrap: wrap; max-width: 860px;
}
.fuel-side { flex: 1; min-width: 240px; }
.fuel-label-top {
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em; margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.fuel-tank {
  position: relative; width: 100%; height: 180px;
  border: 2px solid currentColor; border-radius: 4px;
  overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.fuel-fill {
  position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  transition: height 1.5s cubic-bezier(0.25, 1, 0.5, 1);
  display: flex; align-items: flex-end; justify-content: center;
  padding-bottom: 10px;
}
.fuel-pct {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 28px; font-weight: 900; color: white;
}
.fuel-empty { color: var(--accent); }
.fuel-full { color: var(--safe); }
.fuel-items { list-style: none; }
.fuel-items li {
  font-size: 13px; padding: 8px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
}
.fuel-items li::before { font-size: 16px; }

/* ─── SLIDE 6: YOUR FUEL PROMPTS ─── */
#s6 { background: #f5f0ea; }
.prompts-grid { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; margin-top: 32px; max-width: 720px; }
.prompt-item {
  background: white; padding: 22px 28px;
  border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
  display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px;
  opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-20px);
  transition: opacity 0.5s ease, transform 0.5s ease;
}
.prompt-item.show { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
.pnum {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 32px; font-weight: 900;
  color: rgba(201,70,46,0.2); line-height: 1; flex-shrink: 0; width: 30px;
}
.prompt-item h4 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.prompt-item p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); max-width: none; margin: 0; }

/* ─── SLIDE 7: THE LOG ─── */
#s7 { background: var(--ink); }
.log-card {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  padding: 32px; max-width: 600px; width: 100%;
  margin-top: 32px; position: relative;
}
.log-header {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--cream);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  padding-bottom: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.log-row {
  display: flex; gap: 16px; justify-content: space-between;
  font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  padding: 10px 0;
}
.log-val { color: var(--cream); font-weight: 600; }
.log-val.locked { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); font-style: italic; }
.lock-badge {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
  background: rgba(201,70,46,0.2); border: 1px solid rgba(201,70,46,0.3);
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-size: 11px; padding: 4px 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 20px;
}
.log-today {
  margin-top: 20px; padding: 16px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); font-style: italic;
  border-left: 2px solid var(--accent);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* ─── SLIDE 8: FACILITATOR NOTES ─── */
#s8 { background: #fffdf8; }
.notes-frame {
  max-width: 780px; width: 100%; margin-top: 28px;
}
.notes-banner {
  background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream);
  padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
}
.notes-body {
  background: white; border: 1px solid #e8e0d4;
  border-top: none; padding: 28px;
}
.note-item {
  display: flex; gap: 16px; padding: 14px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #f0ece6;
  opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px);
  transition: opacity 0.4s ease, transform 0.4s ease;
}
.note-item.show { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.note-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.note-bullet {
  width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: rgba(201,70,46,0.1); color: var(--accent);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;
}
.note-item h4 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.note-item p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); max-width: none; margin: 0; }

/* ─── SLIDE 8: TODAY'S TASK ─── */
#s8 { background: var(--accent); }
#s8 h2 { color: white; }
#s8 .label { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }
.task-box {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
  padding: 32px; max-width: 700px; margin-top: 32px;
}
.task-list { list-style: none; margin-top: 16px; }
.task-list li {
  display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 14px;
  padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  font-size: 15px; color: white;
}
.task-list li:last-child { border: none; }
.task-check {
  width: 26px; height: 26px; border-radius: 50%;
  border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; cursor: pointer;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  transition: all 0.2s;
}
.task-check.checked { background: white; border-color: white; color: var(--accent); font-size: 13px; }
.task-min {
  margin-top: 24px; padding: 16px;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
  font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-style: italic;
}

/* ─── SLIDE 9: CLOSE ─── */
#s9 {
  background: var(--ink);
  background-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 70%, rgba(232,160,48,0.12) 0%, transparent 50%);
}
#s9 h2 { color: var(--cream); }
#s9 .body { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); max-width: 540px; }
.close-streak {
  margin-top: 40px; display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  max-width: 700px;
}
.streak-day {
  width: 48px; height: 48px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  transition: all 0.3s;
}
.streak-day.lit {
  background: var(--accent);
  border-color: var(--accent); color: white;
  box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(201,70,46,0.4);
}
.next-up {
  margin-top: 40px; padding: 20px 28px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(232,160,48,0.3);
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; max-width: 600px;
}
.nxt-label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent2); margin-bottom: 4px; }
.nxt-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--cream); }
.nxt-arrow {
  margin-left: auto; font-size: 24px; color: var(--accent2);
  cursor: pointer; transition: transform 0.2s;
}
.nxt-arrow:hover { transform: translateX(4px); }

@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .expect-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .two-path { flex-direction: column; }
  .fuel-diagram { flex-direction: column; }
  .journey-track { gap: 0; }
  .jconnect { min-width: 16px; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HEADER -->
<header>
  <div class="logo">The Unmuted Voice</div>
  <div class="nav-pills" id="pills"></div>
  <div class="day-badge">Day 1 / 30</div>
</header>
<div id="prog"></div>

<!-- NAV -->
<button class="nav-arrow" id="nav-prev" onclick="go(-1)">←</button>
<div class="slide-counter" id="counter">1 / 10</div>
<button class="nav-arrow" id="nav-next" onclick="go(1)">→</button>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- SLIDE 1: HERO -->
<!-- ══════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="slide" id="s1" data-idx="0">
  <div class="day-number">1</div>
  <div style="max-width:860px; width:100%; position:relative; z-index:2;">
    <div class="label label-accent">Day 1 — Welcome</div>
    <div class="theme-pill">
      ✦ This is not another speaking challenge. This is a performance reset.
    </div>
    <h1 style="color:var(--cream)">Welcome to<br><span style="color:var(--accent)">The Unmuted<br>Voice Challenge.</span></h1>
    <p class="body" style="margin-top:16px;">Before we get into any tools, exercises, or deeper work — there is one thing you need to understand clearly.</p>
    <button class="btn" onclick="go(1)">Begin Day 1 →</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- SLIDE 2: WHAT TO EXPECT -->
<!-- ══════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="slide" id="s2" data-idx="1">
  <div style="max-width:900px; width:100%;">
    <div class="label">What to Expect</div>
    <h2>A 30-Day Process.<br><span class="accent-text">Two Distinct Phases.</span></h2>
    <p class="lead">This is not a content experience. It is training. Here is what the full journey looks like — and where Day 1 sits inside it.</p>

    <div class="expect-grid" id="expectGrid" style="grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; max-width:760px;">
      <div class="expect-card" style="grid-column:1;">
        <div class="ec-num">01</div>
        <h4>Days 1–7 · Awareness & Activation</h4>
        <p>See what has actually been happening when you speak under pressure. Map the gap. Name the pattern. Get your first tools. That is what this week is for.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="expect-card" style="grid-column:2;">
        <div class="ec-num">02</div>
        <h4>Days 8–30 · Repetition & Installation</h4>
        <p>The next 23 days are not new lessons every day. They are repetitions of what you now know — applied to real moments, at increasing stakes.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top:24px; padding:18px 24px; background:white; border-left:3px solid var(--accent2); max-width:760px;">
      <p style="font-size:14px; margin:0; color:var(--muted);">Insight can wake you up. <strong style="color:var(--ink);">Repetition is what makes the new version feel familiar.</strong> Do not approach this like content. Approach it like training.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- SLIDE 3: THE JOURNEY MAP -->
<!-- ══════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="slide" id="s3" data-idx="2">
  <div style="max-width:900px; width:100%;">
    <div class="label">Your Mapped Journey</div>
    <h2>7 Days.<br><span class="accent-text">7 Milestones.</span></h2>
    <p class="lead">Each day builds directly on the one before. You are not collecting lessons — you are assembling a single method.</p>

    <div class="journey-track" id="journeyTrack">
      <div class="jstep">
        <div class="jnode current">1</div>
        <div class="jlabel now">Entry &amp;<br>Initiation</div>
      </div>
      <div class="jconnect" style="background:linear-gradient(to right, var(--accent), rgba(201,70,46,0.4));"></div>
      <div class="jstep">
        <div class="jnode upcoming">2</div>
        <div class="jlabel">The Voice<br>Gap</div>
      </div>
      <div class="jconnect" style="background:rgba(201,70,46,0.2)"></div>
      <div class="jstep">
        <div class="jnode upcoming">3</div>
        <div class="jlabel">Map the<br>Trigger</div>
      </div>
      <div class="jconnect" style="background:rgba(201,70,46,0.15)"></div>
